        <h2 class="desc">
          AS A 501(C)(3) NON-PROFIT ORGANIZATION REGISTERED IN THE STATE OF DE,
          WE ARE SUPPORTED BY AN ACCOUNTING AND LEGAL TEAM IN NEW YORK.
        </h2>
